  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "Baremetrics - Stripe Analytics" %></title>

    <meta name="description" content="Baremetrics provides easy, one-click Stripe analytics and metrics for your business.">

    <script type="text/javascript" src="//use.typekit.net/ser3inc.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}</script>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "marketing" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "vendor/custom.modernizr" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "vendor/zepto" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= yield(:head) %>
    <%= render "shared/segment" %>
  </head>

  <body class="marketing">
    <section class="top_bar">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns">
          <div class="logo left">Baremetrics</div>
          <nav class="right">
            <ul class="inline-list">
              <li><a href="#metrics" title="Metrics">Metrics</a></li>
              <li><a href="/demo" title="Metrics" target="_blank">Demo</a></li>
              <li><a href="#testimonials" title="Testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
              <li><a href="#pricing" title="Pricing & Signup">Pricing & Signup</a></li>
              <li><a href="/login" title="Log in">Log in</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="callout">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns text-center">
          <h1>SaaS Analytics for <span>Stripe</span></h1>
          <h2><b>One click</b> and you get <b>dozens of valuable metrics</b> from your Stripe account</h2>
          <%= image_tag 'marketing/img-screenshot.png' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="one_thing" id="one_thing">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns text-center">
          <h3>We’re not kidding about the “one click” thing</h3>
          <p><%= link_to "Sign up now <span>See how easy it really is</span>".html_safe, '#pricing', class: 'button success radius large' %></p>
          <h4>Log in, connect your Stripe account and BOOM! Analytics.<br> <b>Clear, useful, actionable metrics.</b> You’re welcome.</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="metrics" id="metrics">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-10 small-12 large-centered columns text-center">
          <h3>Metrics you can act on</h3>
          <h4>Juicy bits we give you right out of the box with <b>zero configuration</b></h4>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <ul class="large-4 small-12 columns">
              <li>Gross Revenue</li>
              <li>Net Revenue</li>
              <li>Total Fees</li>
              <li>Active Accounts</li>
              <li>Lifetime Value</li>
              <li>Churn</li>
              <li>Average Daily Revenue</li>
              <li>Cancelled Accounts</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="large-4 small-12 columns">
              <li>Annual Run Rate</li>
              <li>Refunds</li>
              <li>Monthly Reurring Revenue</li>
              <li>Average Revenue Per User</li>
              <li>Revenue Growth Rate</li>
              <li>Customer Growth Rate</li>
              <li>ARPU Growth Rate</li>
              <li>Revenue Lost to Coupons</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="large-4 small-12 columns">
              <li>Downgrades</li>
              <li>Upgrades</li>
              <li>Per-plan Customer Count</li>
              <li>Per-plan LTV</li>
              <li>Per-plan Churn</li>
              <li>Per-plan Gross Revenue</li>
              <li>Per-plan Fees</li>
              <li><i>...and more on the way!</i></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-10 small-12 large-centered columns text-center">
          <h3>Happy Customers</h3>
          <h4>Here's what a few of our happy customers have to say about us.</h4>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <div class="large-2 columns">
              <%= image_tag "marketing/img-testimonial-max.jpg", class: 'avatar' %>
            </div>
            <div class="large-10 columns">
              <p>In just one week, Baremetrics helped us <b>grow MRR by 15%</b> through simple insights into our pricing plans. It's becoming our <b>#1 tool for optimizing our SaaS business</b>.</p>
              <p class="byline">&mdash; Max Lynch <%= link_to image_tag("marketing/img-logo-drifty.png"), "http://drifty.com" %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <div class="large-2 push-10 columns">
              <%= image_tag "marketing/img-testimonial-ian.jpg", class: 'avatar' %>
            </div>
            <div class="large-10 pull-2 columns">
              <p>Before I found Baremetrics we were about to spend thousands of dollars in development time figuring out metrics formulas and building reports. For a few dollars a month and 5 seconds of time <b>Baremetrics gave us the same reports with no work at all</b>.</p>
              <p class="byline text-right">&mdash; Ian Landsman <%= link_to image_tag("marketing/img-logo-snappy.png"), "http://www.besnappy.com" %> </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <div class="large-2 columns">
              <%= image_tag "marketing/img-testimonial-alex.jpg", class: 'avatar' %>
            </div>
            <div class="large-10 columns">
              <p>"One click" setup that actually delivers. Literally one click, and boom, the business stats that I've been fighting to figure out on my own were there on my screen. <b>Worth every penny.</b></p>
              <p class="byline">&mdash; Alex Hillman <%= link_to image_tag("marketing/img-logo-indy-hall.png"), "http://www.indyhall.org" %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <div class="large-2 push-10 columns">
              <%= image_tag "marketing/img-testimonial-allan.jpg", class: 'avatar' %>
            </div>
            <div class="large-10 pull-2 columns">
              <p>Click, click, click, then BOOM now you see churn, lifetime customer value and dozens of other <b>stats you need to run your SaaS business</b>.</p>
              <p class="byline text-right">&mdash; Allan Branch <%= link_to image_tag("marketing/img-logo-lessaccounting.png"), "https://lessaccounting.com" %> </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr>
          <div class="row text-left">
            <div class="large-2 columns">
              <%= image_tag "marketing/img-testimonial-paul.jpg", class: 'avatar' %>
            </div>
            <div class="large-10 columns">
              <p>We had been generating all these numbers by hand, once a month. Baremetrics <b>saves us hours</b>, and means we can have the numbers any time we need them.</p>
              <p class="byline">&mdash; Paul Biggar <%= link_to image_tag("marketing/img-logo-circleci.png"), "https://circleci.com" %> </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

