          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="large-8 small-12 large-centered text-center columns enterprise_note">
              <p>Need a larger plan, more team members or a higher level of support? <b><%= mail_to "hello@baremetrics.io", "Send us an email" %></b>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="large-12 columns">
              <div class="widget free_blurb">
                <div class="content text-center">
                  <h4>Less than 50 paying customers?</h4>
                  <p>Realistically, the kind of data we provide isn't that useful for less than 50 monthly recurring paying customers. So, instead of charging you for data that isn't all that useful, <b>we're working on a FREE plan</b> with basic metrics and monthly reports just for folks like you who are just getting their business off the ground! Stay tuned. This will be available very soon.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

